me.tatarka.ipromise

Class Channel<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.tatarka.ipromise.Channel<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of a message

    public class Channel<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A Channel is the producer end of a Progress. An asynchronous method creates a Channel and returns Progress, then calls send(Object) to update the progress.
